-- Spain May Request EU, IMF Loans to Help Banks, Expansion Says
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-01-04T08:32:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-04/spain-may-request-eu-imf-loans-to-help-banks-expansion-says.html
Spanish Prime Minister  Mariano Rajoy ’s government is considering applying for loans from the
European Union’s rescue fund and the International Monetary Fund
to finance the restructuring of the country’s financial
industry,  Expansion  reported, citing unidentified people with
knowledge of the matter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
